Table: Tourney
ID [auto-increment int]
tourney_name [string]
rounds [int]
maxNumber [int]
players [comma-delimited string of Users.ID]  not sure how to fix, need list of participants, maybe user_name over userID?
start_time [datetime]

Table: TourneyRound
ID [auto-increment int]
tourney [Tourney ID]
round [int]
fights [comma-delimited string of TourneyFight.ID]  not sure how to fix, may not need this

Table: TourneyFight
ID [auto-increment int]
tourney_round [tourneyroundID]
homeID [Users.ID]
awayID [Users.ID]
winner [Users.ID]
score [string]
completed_time [datetime]

Table: Users
ID [auto-increment int]
username [string]
password [encrypted string]
display_name [string]
last_login [datetime]
last_tourney [Tourney.ID]
